{"tid":1432414,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"敵疲我打！紅媒狙撃，TVB股價、收視齊失禁","createTime":"2019-08-08T08:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T09:45:31.000Z","uid":267881,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"69c0e6e1b49f5a973887cb9197c76c676e94bdc7","tid":1432414,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:39:36.000Z","msg":"節錄自「抵制TVB運動」<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://facebook.com/banTVB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2FbanTVB&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2FGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=e5414fdd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/banTVB</a><br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"https://t.me/noTVB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FnoTVB&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2FGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=df934d9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/noTVB</a> @noTVB<br />\n<br />\n無綫的收視持續下跌，昨日無綫公佈7月22日至28日的收視成績，可謂慘不忍睹，一向深得觀眾支持的《愛&middot;回家之開心速遞》，竟然跌破25點，跨平台總收視只有24.4點（約157萬觀眾收看），相信是近半年來的新低點。譚俊彥和張振朗的新劇《包青天再起風雲》首周播出，不過跨平台總收視只有21.9點（約144萬觀眾收看），暫時成為19年無綫黃金檔三線劇首周最低收視的劇集。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTVB股價逆市跌2.15%，繼續在十年低位俳佪<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/JvSC2QN/EBBD4546-36-EE-4-EF6-B421-93-E2-E291-F40-B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FJvSC2QN%2FEBBD4546-36-EE-4-EF6-B421-93-E2-E291-F40-B.jpg&h=b0a7286e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抵制TVB運動，包括：<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 呼籲身邊人罷看TVB，以後TVB任何節目都不看<br />\n2. 一人一信向通訊局投訴TVB，將投訴數字創新高<br />\n3. 呼籲商人拒絕在TVB落廣告<br />\n4. 呼籲餐廳老闆不要播放TVB<br />\n5. 呼籲各商場不要與TVB合作搞活動<br />\n我們支持良心商戶，會多作消費</span><br />\n<br />\n誠邀各界加入「監察TVB行動組」🔬<br />\nFacebook: <a href=\"https://facebook.com/groups/banTVBteam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2Fgroups%2FbanTVBteam&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2FGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=8f2ba5b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/groups/banTVBteam</a><br />\nTelegram: <a href=\"https://t.me/noTVBteam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FnoTVBteam&d=g7cViP25SqI%2F%2FE6cIGpO7%2FGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=fdbc750e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/noTVBteam</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n愈接近成功愈唔可以停！"},{"pid":"48f809fbc16cc04e50cd8762d3b66cfeb72d625f","tid":1432414,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:41:23.000Z","msg":"跨平台總收視只有21.9點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nmytv人手refresh + 作大既商場收視都計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3561c339373be2b2b6e866e6b4004584c687b104","tid":1432414,"uid":293066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:42:55.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dafc2909b32c4a549d74b06bbdde2e3ad31e4461","tid":1432414,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:45:20.000Z","msg":"繼續努力 打到cctvb仆街"},{"pid":"166193798cf2beabbdf2f0bc94263e7e4c757ee1","tid":1432414,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:47:42.000Z","msg":"快D去廣告商facebook分享下用後感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ab81127ff8b0ef5887c4439f92966c49291879","tid":1432414,"uid":281895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:48:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1320101/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1320101/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊做轉台師"},{"pid":"f65764245ec039c2ce28ee6f843f3df263c6ed85","tid":1432414,"uid":83041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T08:51:51.000Z","m